V0508_01_00_00_0.text: If you get in my way, you're forcing me to defeat you!

V0508_01_00_01_0.text: Once you step into my battlefield, be prepared to lose!

V0508_01_00_02_0.text: My Duel is superior to yours!

V0508_01_00_03_0.text: If you really wanna fight, let's do it!

V0508_01_00_04_0.text:
Hurry up.
There are plenty others I need to take down!

V0508_01_00_06_0.text: I'll see just how tough you are!

V0508_01_00_07_0.text: I'll do anything to protect the children in my city!

V0508_01_00_08_0.text:
You KO'ed me before.
But this time, I'm knocking you out!

V0508_01_00_09_0.text: I remember a time when you couldn't do anything without me.

V0508_01_00_10_0.text: I know exactly how your deck works, so you can't win!

V0508_03_00_01_0.text: You're not Dueling with heart or conviction.

V0508_03_00_03_0.text: No matter what you play, I'll destroy it!

V0508_03_00_04_0.text: You won't defeat me that easily!

V0508_03_00_05_0.text: You may be breaking my cards, but you won't break me!

V0508_05_00_00_0.text: Pushing me to my breaking point only makes me fight harder!

V0508_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0508_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0508_11_08_01_0.text:
I build the Overlay Network!
Xyz Summon!

V0508_16_00_00_0.text: There's nothing in your final moments but suffering!

V0508_16_00_01_0.text: With this last strike, you're finished!

V0508_21_00_00_0.text:
You found a way to survive.
Barely.

V0508_21_00_01_0.text:
I'm not here for fun.
I'm here to fight!

V0508_21_00_04_0.text: Even if I'm on the edge of defeat, you won't break me!

V0508_21_00_05_0.text:
Surrender?
That word isn't in my dictionary!

V0508_28_00_00_0.text:
Heh.
Your skills were mediocre at best.

V0508_28_00_01_0.text: I can tell you've never faced real combat in your life.

V0508_28_00_02_0.text: You need an iron will to win - which you don't have.

V0508_28_00_03_0.text: You picked the wrong prey to hunt.

V0508_28_00_04_0.text: Not everyone deserves my best, but I always give my all.

V0508_28_00_05_0.text:
You talk a big game.
But you don't play one.

V0508_28_00_06_0.text:
Your Xyz Summon was nothing special.
Believe me - I'd know.

V0508_28_00_07_0.text:
I fight everyday just to survive.
So you can never scare me.

V0508_28_00_08_0.text:
Life isn't easy.
But none is tougher than mine!

V0508_28_00_09_0.text: I only made it this far because I have a friend like you.

V0508_28_00_10_0.text:
Work on your endgame.
Or you'll never defeat me.

V0508_29_00_00_0.text: Where did you learn to Duel like that?

V0508_29_00_01_0.text: You used techniques that can only be learned in combat.

V0508_29_00_02_0.text: I always come back to defeat my foes!

V0508_29_00_02_1.text: You've proven you can do the same!

V0508_29_00_04_0.text: You're really from the Leo Institute?

V0508_29_00_05_0.text:
You KO'ed me again...
Well done, Yuto.

V0508_29_00_06_0.text:
Now I know for sure.
Only Lulu Duels like this.

V0508_30_00_00_0.text: Wherever I go turns into a battlefield!

V0508_30_00_01_0.text: I don't sense any fire in your Duel.

V0508_34_00_00_0.text: If you want revenge, take me down!

V0508_34_00_01_0.text: Only the unbreakable can survive the worst!

V0508_34_00_02_0.text: If you want to mix things up, pick up an Action Card.

V0508_34_00_03_0.text: You're trying to mess with my mind to get the advantage.

V0508_34_00_04_0.text:
Just quit.
This Duel is over!

V0508_34_00_05_0.text:
Calm down.
This isn't your battlefield.

V0508_34_00_06_0.text: Are you from the Leo Institute?

V0508_34_00_09_0.text: Do you now know how it feels to be hunted?

V0508_34_00_10_0.text: Why is Lulu here... Was she able to escape on her own?

V0508_34_00_11_0.text:
Get set to strike!
Fire one!

V0508_34_00_12_0.text:
For my friends whose souls you took!
Fire two!

V0508_34_00_13_0.text:
For Lulu!
Cowards who feed on the weak will pay!
Fire three!

V0508_34_00_14_0.text:
Feel my fury!
For Yuto!
Fire four!

V0508_34_00_15_0.text:
Your suffering still won’t make up for the pain!
Fire five!

V0508_36_00_00_0.text: Feel free to do whatever you like!

V0508_36_00_02_0.text:
Sorry.
I need you to take over.

V0508_36_00_05_0.text: Yuya, I leave the rest to you.

V0508_36_00_06_0.text:
Sorry Gong.
But you can fix this.

V0508_08_00_00_0.text:

Raidraptor - Call!

V0508_08_00_01_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Spell!
Raidraptor - Nest!

V0508_08_00_04_0.text: Skip Force's effect activates from the Graveyard!

My Quick-Play Spell!
Rank-Up-Magic Doom Double Force!

V0508_08_00_07_0.text: The Quick-Play Spell, Rank-Up-Magic Raptor's Force!

V0508_08_00_09_0.text: I activate Raid Force's effect from the Graveyard!

V0508_08_00_10_0.text:
My Quick-Play Spell!
Rank-Up-Magic Revolution Force!

V0508_08_00_11_0.text: I'll rescue every ally that you captured!

V0508_08_00_12_0.text:
My Quick-Play Spell!
Phantom Knights' Rank-Up-Magic Force!

V0508_08_00_13_0.text:
I activate my Equip Spell!
Raptor's Ultimate Mace!

V0508_08_00_15_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Unicorn Beacon!

V0508_08_00_16_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Raidraptor Replica!

V0508_08_00_17_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Raidraptor - Return!

V0508_08_00_18_0.text: I banish Raidraptor - Return from my Grave to activate it!

V0508_08_00_19_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Raidraptor - Readiness!

V0508_08_00_20_0.text: I banish Raidraptor - Readiness from my Graveyard!

V0508_08_00_21_0.text:
I play my Counter Trap!
Raidraptor's Phantom Knights Claw!

V0508_08_00_22_0.text:
I activate my Counter Trap!
Raptor's Gust!

V0508_08_00_23_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Raider's Unbreakable Mind!

V0508_08_00_25_0.text: Unbreakable Mind activates when it's destroyed by an effect!

V0508_09_00_07_1.text: Everyone you hunted will now unleash their fury!

V0508_09_00_09_0.text: Arsenal Falcon activates when it goes to the Graveyard!

V0508_09_00_10_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Revolution Falcon's effect!

V0508_09_00_10_1.text: The will of the fallen unite to annihilate their foes!

V0508_09_00_12_0.text: Revolution Falcon has a Raidraptor as an Overlay Unit!

V0508_09_00_12_1.text: Scorch 'em in the fires of revolution!

V0508_09_00_13_0.text: Xyz Summoning Air Raid activates its effect!

V0508_09_00_13_1.text: Burn in the flames of the rebellion!

V0508_09_00_14_0.text: Revolution Falcon - Air Raid activates when it's destroyed!

V0508_09_00_15_0.text: Blaze Falcon's effect activates when it deals battle damage!

V0508_09_00_16_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Blaze Falcon's effect!

V0508_09_00_18_0.text: Stranger Falcon's effect activates when it's destroyed!

V0508_09_00_23_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Raider's Knight's effect!

V0508_09_00_27_0.text: Skull Eagle's effect activates when it's used to Summon!

V0508_09_00_33_0.text: Fuzzy Lanius activates when it's sent to the Graveyard!

V0508_09_00_34_0.text: I activate Raidraptor - Booster Strix's effect from my hand!

V0508_09_00_35_0.text: Raidraptor - Pain Lanius's effect activates from my hand!

V0508_09_00_36_0.text: Raidraptor - Last Strix activates its effect from my hand!

V0508_09_00_41_0.text: I banish Heel Eagle from my Graveyard to use its effect!

V0508_09_00_43_0.text: I activate Strangle Lanius's effect from my hand!

V0508_09_00_47_0.text: I banish Mimicry Lanius from my Graveyard to use its effect!

V0508_37_00_00_0.text:
Soar on wings of courage!
Talons ready for the rebellion!

V0508_13_00_00_0.text: Witness the ascent of Rank 4 Raidraptor - Rise Falcon!

V0508_37_00_01_0.text:
The phoenix doesn't rise from the ashes!
It's the raptor!

V0508_13_00_01_0.text: Fly high, Rank 12 Raidraptor - Final Fortress Falcon!

V0508_37_00_02_0.text: Witness the next evolutionary step in my aerial arsenal!

V0508_13_00_02_0.text:
Rise up!
Rank 10 Raidraptor - Ultimate Falcon!

V0508_37_00_03_0.text: To stay in the game, you have to keep pushing to the edge!

V0508_13_00_03_0.text:
Cleared for takeoff!
Raidraptor - Satellite Cannon Falcon!

V0508_13_00_04_0.text:
Take to the skies!
Rank 7 Raidraptor - Arsenal Falcon!

V0508_37_00_04_0.text: Set your wings ablaze and lock your gaze on our foe!

V0508_13_00_06_0.text:
Emerge!
Rank 6 Raidraptor - Revolution Falcon - Air Raid!

V0508_37_00_05_0.text:
Terror of the skies!
Predator of blazing force!

V0508_13_00_07_0.text:
Rise up!
Rank 5 Raidraptor - Blaze Falcon!

V0508_37_00_06_0.text: Unleash your secret power hidden in your ferocious wings!

V0508_37_00_07_0.text: By hunting me down, you’ve become the hunted instead!

V0508_13_00_09_0.text:
Rise to the sky!
Rank 4 Raidraptor - Force Strix!

V0508_37_00_08_0.text:
Blaze with crimson light!
Set flame to light my soul!

V0508_13_00_13_0.text:
Let's go!
Link 2 Raidraptor - Wise Strix!

V0508_13_00_32_0.text: With this card, Saya taught me about true friendship.

V0508_19_00_00_0.text:
Raidraptor - Rise Falcon!
Break through their lines!

V0508_19_00_03_0.text:
Satellite Cannon Falcon!
Get set to strike!

V0508_19_00_03_1.text: For all the victims you hunted down - this is payback!

V0508_19_00_05_0.text:
Go, Revolution Falcon!
Avenge those who have fallen!

V0508_19_00_06_1.text:
Feel the flames of revolution!
Blitzing Bombardment!

V0508_19_00_07_1.text: Charge your wings and fire an electrostatic bolt!

V0508_44_00_02_0.text: Only one will rule the Duel...

V0508_44_00_03_0.text: In the ultimate fusion of monsters and mayhem!

V0508_27_00_02_0.text: You won't get away with that...
